---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Red Fox Inn — Lancaster, New Hampshire | White Mountains Lodging"
  description="A 27-room independently operated inn on Main Street in Lancaster, NH. Between the White Mountain National Forest and the Connecticut River."
>
  <main>
    <section class="relative min-h-[85vh] flex items-center justify-center px-6 bg-fox-brown text-snow">
      <div class="max-w-4xl text-center py-24">
        <p class="font-body text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-fox-orange mb-6 font-medium">
          Lancaster, New Hampshire &middot; Chartered 1763
        </p>
        <h1 class="font-display font-light text-5xl md:text-7xl leading-[1.05] mb-8 text-snow">
          A new chapter<br />on an old road.
        </h1>
        <p class="font-body text-lg md:text-xl text-fox-cream max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-10 leading-relaxed font-light">
          Twenty-seven rooms on Main Street, three blocks from a 1913 bronze fox, and five minutes from the mountain a boy from this town protected for the rest of us.
        </p>
        <a
          href="#book"
          class="font-body inline-block px-10 py-3.5 bg-fox-red text-snow font-medium tracking-wide hover:bg-deep-red transition-colors"
        >
          Check Availability
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="px-6 py-28 bg-snow">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
        <p class="font-body text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-fox-red mb-6 font-medium">The Story</p>
        <h2 class="font-display font-light text-4xl md:text-5xl mb-10 leading-[1.1]">
          Clever, caring, independent,<br />and at home with the wild.
        </h2>
        <p class="font-body text-lg text-warm-gray leading-relaxed mb-6 font-light">
          When Lancaster turned 150 in 1913, the town commissioned a bronze fox from <em class="font-display text-fox-brown">Anna Vaughn Hyatt Huntington</em> &mdash; the same sculptor whose Joan of Arc stands in Riverside Park and whose El Cid guards the Hispanic Society in Manhattan.
        </p>
        <p class="font-body text-lg text-warm-gray leading-relaxed font-light">
          It still rests in Centennial Park at Main and School, three blocks from our front door. We borrowed our name from it.
        </p>
        <a
          href="/story/"
          class="font-body inline-block mt-10 text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-fox-red border-b border-fox-orange pb-1 font-medium hover:text-deep-red hover:border-deep-red transition-colors"
        >
          Read the full story
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="px-6 py-28 bg-fox-cream">
      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
        <p class="font-body text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-fox-red mb-6 text-center font-medium">Experience</p>
        <h2 class="font-display font-light text-4xl md:text-5xl mb-14 text-center leading-[1.1]">
          The White Mountains<br />from Main Street.
        </h2>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-12">
          <div>
            <p class="font-display font-light text-3xl mb-2 text-fox-red">5 min</p>
            <p class="font-body uppercase tracking-[0.15em] text-xs text-fox-orange mb-3 font-medium">Weeks State Park</p>
            <p class="font-body text-warm-gray leading-relaxed font-light">The 1912 fieldstone lodge of the senator who wrote the act that created the White Mountain National Forest.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="font-display font-light text-3xl mb-2 text-fox-red">15 min</p>
            <p class="font-body uppercase tracking-[0.15em] text-xs text-fox-orange mb-3 font-medium">Santa's Village</p>
            <p class="font-body text-warm-gray leading-relaxed font-light">A working Christmas park since 1953. One of the few places in New England that still feels exactly like it did when it opened.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="font-display font-light text-3xl mb-2 text-fox-red">45 min</p>
            <p class="font-body uppercase tracking-[0.15em] text-xs text-fox-orange mb-3 font-medium">Bretton Woods</p>
            <p class="font-body text-warm-gray leading-relaxed font-light">Omni Mount Washington Resort, Cog Railway, and the notch where Franconia opens to Cannon.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <footer class="px-6 py-20 bg-night text-fox-cream text-sm">
      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-12">
        <div>
          <p class="font-display font-light text-3xl text-snow mb-4">Red Fox Inn</p>
          <p class="font-body leading-relaxed font-light">
            112 Main Street<br />Lancaster, NH 03584
          </p>
          <p class="font-body mt-4">
            <a href="tel:+16037884921" class="hover:text-fox-amber transition-colors">(603) 788&#8209;4921</a>
          </p>
          <p class="font-body">
            <a href="mailto:stay@redfoxinnnh.com" class="hover:text-fox-amber transition-colors">stay@redfoxinnnh.com</a>
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="font-body uppercase text-xs tracking-[0.2em] text-fox-orange mb-4 font-medium">Visit</p>
          <ul class="font-body space-y-2 font-light">
            <li><a href="/stay/" class="hover:text-snow transition-colors">Stay</a></li>
            <li><a href="/experience/" class="hover:text-snow transition-colors">Experience</a></li>
            <li><a href="/journal/" class="hover:text-snow transition-colors">Journal</a></li>
            <li><a href="/story/" class="hover:text-snow transition-colors">Story</a></li>
            <li><a href="/policies/" class="hover:text-snow transition-colors">Policies</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="font-body uppercase text-xs tracking-[0.2em] text-fox-orange mb-4 font-medium">The fine print</p>
          <p class="font-body leading-relaxed font-light">
            A 27-room independent inn in Coös County, New Hampshire. Between the White Mountain National Forest and the Connecticut River.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </footer>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
